The game layout should be maintained on all screens.
The landing screen should allow a user to select a specific save file to continue (or start a new one)
After logging in, the screen should consist of a header banner and a 2 pane layout with a smaller left pane for navigation and a larger right pane for the main game actions.
The game should have a dark color scheme by default - dark greys and light teal accents. Main text can be white or very light grey. the font should be a generic sans serif for legitibility.

Links in the left nav should include:
- Home
- Armory
- Temple
- Training Grounds
- Tepke Mines

Other links will appear in this list, but are not "unlocked" by default.